RobotWare¶

set_zonedata(self, var, zonedata)¶

Set the value for a zonedata variable in RAPID. var: name of variable as declared in RAPID. zonedata: desired zonedata value [int].

set_speeddata(self, var, speeddata)¶

Set the value [int] for a speeddata variable in RAPID. var: name of variable as declared in RAPID. speeddata: desired speeddata value [int].

set_speed_ratio(self, speed_ratio)¶

Set the speed ratio of the robot. speed_ratio: desired speed ratio in percent [1-100].
